{"tid":1363604,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"光復元朗，勢在必行，一切嚴重後果將由警方全部負責。","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:23:31.000Z","uid":254898,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e56438de59c44725c2b332dd9faa9e1199549c7","tid":1363604,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"係時候推元朗post啦。<br />\n有冇不反對通知書都好，<br />\n今次元朗事件令人髮指，<br />\n好多人都有表態。<br />\n包括唔小之前仲未表態既kol，<br />\n佢地都表曬態啦！<br />\n只要一股作氣，光復元朗規模理應更大！<br />\n我地亦有必要推得比以往大，<br />\n因為今次面對既係鄉黑，<br />\n元朗既路同面積亦比其他地區大同複雜。<br />\n但係眼見而家就比D5毛解放軍post擾敵，<br />\n好多人連27定28，幾點出都唔清楚，<br />\n得翻一日時間咋，快D集中火力，搞掂元朗先啦。"},{"pid":"7502adbdf86c11d0d15353b15afb010709df2ab1","tid":1363604,"uid":289303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c813be555a4eb58d774cb02c124970c8f5bee47","tid":1363604,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVPnWaj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVPnWaj.gif&h=94ed5383&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c30d37849b5d131eda80e209668894353f19e27","tid":1363604,"uid":272898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"元朗公園<br />\n我見個個星期都好多菲傭野餐"},{"pid":"90a7b9cf52b75e30db10b5128afdf84988cbb330","tid":1363604,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c30d37849b5d131eda80e209668894353f19e27","tid":1363604,"uid":272898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"元朗公園<br />\n我見個個星期都好多菲傭野餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}